@startuml
title State Machine: Evidence State

[*] --> Collected
Collected : Discovered at scene\nInitial documentation

Collected --> Logged : Submitted to evidence
Logged : Entered in system\nChain begins

Logged --> Stored : Placed in secure storage
Stored : In evidence room\nProper conditions

Stored --> CheckedOut : Removed for analysis
CheckedOut : In possession of\nauthorized personnel

CheckedOut --> InAnalysis : At crime lab
InAnalysis : Being tested/analyzed\nScientific examination

InAnalysis --> Analyzed : Testing complete
Analyzed : Results documented\nReady for return

Analyzed --> Stored : Returned to storage
Stored --> CheckedOut : Additional analysis needed

Stored --> InCourt : Presented as exhibit
InCourt : Court proceedings\nUnder court control

InCourt --> Stored : Returned from court

Stored --> Disposed : Final disposition
Disposed : Destroyed/returned\nAccording to policy

Disposed --> [*]
@enduml
